{"tid":1385343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民研:逾三分二受訪者反對林鄭","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T05:45:41.000Z","uid":77196,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"469bb0a27616e8b7896e2eda3d73607b3d15db4c","tid":1385343,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究所發表第二次民調結果，發現特首林鄭月娥的民望指數，較兩星期前的調查下跌3.3分至30.1分，支持率由26%下跌至21%，反對率由上次的66%上升至70%，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">創歷屆行政長官及她上任以來最高</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所主席鍾庭耀表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>林鄭月娥在競選時曾表示如不到主流民意支持將辭任特首，今次調查得出逾三分二受訪者反對林鄭月娥，亦有民間參考價值</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n調查於今月17至19日，以電話隨機訪問1002名市民。調查發現，市民對民生、經濟及政治狀況滿意淨值，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">下跌至1992年有紀錄以來新低</span></strong>，其中政治狀況更為負82個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2204003/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2204003%2F&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=5483f0cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2204003/</a>"},{"pid":"491d2571185a0e8714d5c85a626297148af0fe2e","tid":1385343,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"【急！】港大民研轉型惜捐款STEP-BY-STEP<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276228\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276228</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請支持香港民意研究所(前港大民研) 持續運作！"},{"pid":"02b507b4a93b033a4fd2f6b4868d2007233f8bd4","tid":1385343,"uid":171238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"元朗721仲未發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知仲跌幾多,幾時見底"},{"pid":"0c904796d163f3bcf1f705a5d8536c58761fc9a2","tid":1385343,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02b507b4a93b033a4fd2f6b4868d2007233f8bd4","tid":1385343,"uid":171238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"元朗721仲未發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知仲跌幾多,幾時見底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:45:41.000Z","msg":"低處未算低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}